5
00:00:25,410 --> 00:00:28,599
planning of protected areas,
edited once again by the world commission

6
00:00:28,599 --> 00:00:29,949
of protected areas.

7
00:00:29,949 --> 00:00:33,330
You can also find a lot of information in
